{
  "texts": [
    "From each segmented region, the following features are retained to be used in downstream steps: area, centroid, maximum and average intensity.",
    "This formed a list of candidate spots from each FOV.",
    "Spot filtering.",
    "To control the specificity of the decoding procedure, we augmented the codebook with a number of barcodes (5-10% of the used barcodes) not used in the probe set (empty barcodes).",
    "After spot calling, we record the properties (e.g., area, maximum and average intensity) of spots with an empty barcode."
  ]
}